  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.08,
      "text": "목소리 좋아요 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.08,
      "end": 3.16,
      "text": "Thank you very much"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.16,
      "end": 3.58,
      "text": "Welcome"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.58,
      "end": 5.58,
      "text": "Welcome rise and shine"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.58,
      "end": 7.14,
      "text": "Good morning everyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 7.14,
      "end": 11.1,
      "text": "어머어머 이경아님께서요 메시지를 또 보내주셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.1,
      "end": 12.46,
      "text": "Welcome let me hear"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.46,
      "end": 16.26,
      "text": "우리 크리스씨 등장과 함께 이렇게 칭찬이 일색입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.26,
      "end": 17.62,
      "text": "한번 들어보시겠어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.88,
      "end": 20.38,
      "text": "가래서 자걸래요 문자들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.38,
      "end": 22.34,
      "text": "앞을 싹 빼고"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.34,
      "end": 23.38,
      "text": "그렇지 않아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.38,
      "end": 26.3,
      "text": "자 이경아님께서 주신 메시지는요"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.3,
      "end": 32.98,
      "text": "크리스 우맘이 설명하실 때 한국말로 감칠맛이다 라고 말씀하시는 게 아니라"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.98,
      "end": 36.16,
      "text": "우리말로 감칠맛이다 라고 하시는 거 듣고 놀랬어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.16,
      "end": 38.88,
      "text": "그랬어요 한국에 대한 애정이 느껴지네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.88,
      "end": 41.68,
      "text": "Yeah I was so touched"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.68,
      "end": 43.22,
      "text": "우리말로 하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.22,
      "end": 45.92,
      "text": "그때 저도 기억이 나는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.92,
      "end": 50.0,
      "text": "크리스씨가 한국말로 감칠맛이죠 이렇게 이야기 안 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.0,
      "end": 52.32,
      "text": "우리말로 감칠맛이죠 라고 한 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.32,
      "end": 54.62,
      "text": "저도 그때 되게 감동했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.62,
      "end": 56.72,
      "text": "When I'm explaining things in Korean"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.72,
      "end": 59.04,
      "text": "that kind of expression"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.04,
      "end": 60.44,
      "text": "it just comes out"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.44,
      "end": 62.96,
      "text": "I guess I've been in Korea too long"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.96,
      "end": 65.46,
      "text": "and now it's just like second nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.46,
      "end": 66.46,
      "text": "진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.58,
      "end": 68.06,
      "text": "와 너무 훌륭합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.06,
      "end": 68.86,
      "text": "어쨌든"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.86,
      "end": 71.26,
      "text": "우리 주인공 에이브가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.26,
      "end": 74.12,
      "text": "정말 가족들의 화합을 도모하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.12,
      "end": 75.64,
      "text": "정말 노력을 많이 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.64,
      "end": 78.7,
      "text": "그렇지만 가족들끼리의 갈등은 어때지는 것 같아요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.1,
      "end": 80.38,
      "text": "더 커지는 것만 같죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.38,
      "end": 83.88,
      "text": "It's too hard to do it alone himself"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.88,
      "end": 85.38,
      "text": "I know he's just a kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.38,
      "end": 86.86,
      "text": "He needs to have fun"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.86,
      "end": 88.82,
      "text": "He shouldn't be worried about"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.82,
      "end": 91.8,
      "text": "his family fighting over religion"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.8,
      "end": 94.16,
      "text": "아무리 맛있는 요리를 만들어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.16,
      "end": 95.58,
      "text": "화합이 되지 않는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.58,
      "end": 97.04,
      "text": "그나마 다행인 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.04,
      "end": 100.64,
      "text": "우리 에이브 옆에 동기부여를 해주는 멘토가 있었잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.64,
      "end": 102.68,
      "text": "Oh he has a very important mentor"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.68,
      "end": 103.3,
      "text": "Who's he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.62,
      "end": 104.06,
      "text": "Chico"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.06,
      "end": 105.02,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.02,
      "end": 108.04,
      "text": "Chico is also the name of a famous place in California"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.04,
      "end": 108.74,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.1,
      "end": 109.96,
      "text": "It's also a college"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.96,
      "end": 110.88,
      "text": "Chico"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.88,
      "end": 114.4,
      "text": "So it's an easy to remember name for me"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.4,
      "end": 118.4,
      "text": "And this is the Afro-Brazilian street food chef"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.4,
      "end": 122.26,
      "text": "Who is also Abe's mentor and guide for cooking"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.26,
      "end": 123.18,
      "text": "Yeah that's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.18,
      "end": 125.8,
      "text": "So this is another lesson I learned from it"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.8,
      "end": 128.66,
      "text": "It is important to have a good mentor"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.66,
      "end": 133.14,
      "text": "Or have some good friends or colleagues or people around us"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.14,
      "end": 133.9,
      "text": "For sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.9,
      "end": 134.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.28,
      "end": 134.84,
      "text": "Definitely"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.84,
      "end": 137.62,
      "text": "So do you have a good mentor besides your wife?"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.1,
      "end": 139.0,
      "text": "Besides my wife?"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.0,
      "end": 142.72,
      "text": "Of course my wife is my best ultimate mentor"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.72,
      "end": 143.22,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.22,
      "end": 146.04,
      "text": "Wife 말고 또 다른 멘토가 있다면 누가 있을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.2,
      "end": 147.38,
      "text": "Besides my wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.38,
      "end": 150.78,
      "text": "Well when I fight with my wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.78,
      "end": 152.78,
      "text": "Or I want to leave the house"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.78,
      "end": 153.22,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.22,
      "end": 155.44,
      "text": "I go to my barber"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.44,
      "end": 157.1,
      "text": "My barber"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.1,
      "end": 157.16,
      "text": "My barber"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.16,
      "end": 159.52,
      "text": "He lives right near my house"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.52,
      "end": 160.04,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.04,
      "end": 164.88,
      "text": "I met him on the day of my wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.88,
      "end": 167.54,
      "text": "He did my hair before my wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.54,
      "end": 170.24,
      "text": "And all my friends from the US"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.24,
      "end": 174.18,
      "text": "So I've known him for almost 9 years now"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.18,
      "end": 175.56,
      "text": "10 years almost"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.56,
      "end": 178.22,
      "text": "굉장히 좋은 관계를 계속 유지하고 계시는군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.22,
      "end": 178.68,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.68,
      "end": 182.5,
      "text": "I don't think he's listening"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.5,
      "end": 183.34,
      "text": "But"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.34,
      "end": 187.22,
      "text": "I always tell him that you are amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.22,
      "end": 188.78,
      "text": "강진분인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.78,
      "end": 189.96,
      "text": "형이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.96,
      "end": 193.0,
      "text": "So he advises me about Korean culture"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.0,
      "end": 196.02,
      "text": "And problems with marriage"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.02,
      "end": 197.66,
      "text": "His wife and him"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.66,
      "end": 199.62,
      "text": "They have a very special relationship"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.62,
      "end": 201.1,
      "text": "They're very close"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.1,
      "end": 204.86,
      "text": "Even though they've been married for longer than me"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.86,
      "end": 206.4,
      "text": "So he gives me tips"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.4,
      "end": 208.36,
      "text": "About how to make my wife happy"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.36,
      "end": 212.64,
      "text": "와 진짜 정신적인 그런 지주가 되어주시는 분 중에 한 분이군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.64,
      "end": 213.18,
      "text": "Definitely"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.18,
      "end": 213.94,
      "text": "훌륭합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.94,
      "end": 214.62,
      "text": "How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.82,
      "end": 215.08,
      "text": "Laura"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.08,
      "end": 215.5,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.5,
      "end": 219.5,
      "text": "저는 사실 자주자주 연락은 드리지는 못해도"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.5,
      "end": 223.6,
      "text": "제 마음속에 항상 지주가 되어주시는 지도교수님이 계시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.6,
      "end": 226.68,
      "text": "또 아주 다정한 지인들이 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.68,
      "end": 227.26,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.26,
      "end": 228.76,
      "text": "남편"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.76,
      "end": 229.48,
      "text": "아니"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.48,
      "end": 230.78,
      "text": "생각도 안 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.78,
      "end": 232.66,
      "text": "Sorry"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.66,
      "end": 236.04,
      "text": "자 오늘 장면 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.04,
      "end": 237.66,
      "text": "I don't understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.66,
      "end": 238.54,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.14,
      "end": 239.94,
      "text": "Is this because of me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.16,
      "end": 240.46,
      "text": "Hey"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.46,
      "end": 241.26,
      "text": "Look at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.26,
      "end": 241.9,
      "text": "It is"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.9,
      "end": 242.56,
      "text": "No it's not"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.56,
      "end": 242.96,
      "text": "Look at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.96,
      "end": 243.56,
      "text": "Look at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.56,
      "end": 244.84,
      "text": "I promise you"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.84,
      "end": 245.66,
      "text": "It's not because of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.66,
      "end": 246.9,
      "text": "Sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.9,
      "end": 248.72,
      "text": "Well"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.72,
      "end": 250.36,
      "text": "We think it's best"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.36,
      "end": 251.84,
      "text": "If we just take a little"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.84,
      "end": 252.68,
      "text": "Break"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.68,
      "end": 254.4,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.4,
      "end": 255.14,
      "text": "Now"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.14,
      "end": 257.38,
      "text": "Abe's parents are in crisis"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.38,
      "end": 258.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.42,
      "end": 259.36,
      "text": "Marriage crisis"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.36,
      "end": 260.48,
      "text": "Uh oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.48,
      "end": 261.12,
      "text": "They're"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.12,
      "end": 262.36,
      "text": "They're thinking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.36,
      "end": 263.46,
      "text": "They're not thinking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.46,
      "end": 265.48,
      "text": "They've decided to split up"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.48,
      "end": 267.6,
      "text": "I think they're getting a divorce"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.6,
      "end": 268.06,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.06,
      "end": 272.06,
      "text": "지금 이혼을 준비하는 그런 과정이었던 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.06,
      "end": 272.74,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.74,
      "end": 272.86,
      "text": "어쨌든"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.86,
      "end": 275.48,
      "text": "Abe가 아주 충격이 컸겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.48,
      "end": 275.98,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.98,
      "end": 276.76,
      "text": "So Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.76,
      "end": 277.58,
      "text": "Many kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.58,
      "end": 279.74,
      "text": "They think it's their own fault"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.74,
      "end": 281.46,
      "text": "That their parents are fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.46,
      "end": 283.58,
      "text": "And if they get a divorce"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.58,
      "end": 284.78,
      "text": "They blame themselves"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.78,
      "end": 286.66,
      "text": "Abe is like that"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.66,
      "end": 287.24,
      "text": "Right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.24,
      "end": 287.8,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.8,
      "end": 290.56,
      "text": "자기 때문에 부모님이 지금 싸움이 커지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.56,
      "end": 294.28,
      "text": "지금 헤어지게 된 상황이다라고 생각을 하고 있다는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.28,
      "end": 296.74,
      "text": "진짜 상처가 컸을 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.74,
      "end": 299.12,
      "text": "일단은 중요 표현들 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.12,
      "end": 301.18,
      "text": "Because of"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.18,
      "end": 302.7,
      "text": "Because of"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.7,
      "end": 303.98,
      "text": "뭐 뭐 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.98,
      "end": 306.24,
      "text": "라는 전치사구입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.24,
      "end": 307.86,
      "text": "It's not because of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.86,
      "end": 309.2,
      "text": "It's okay, Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.2,
      "end": 310.98,
      "text": "이것도 되게 좋은 표현이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.98,
      "end": 313.72,
      "text": "그 켈리 클�лар크슨의 팝송 중에"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.72,
      "end": 315.36,
      "text": "Because of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.36,
      "end": 317.1,
      "text": "나도 아는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.1,
      "end": 318.36,
      "text": "Oh, we connected"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.36,
      "end": 321.1,
      "text": "Because of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.1,
      "end": 323.14,
      "text": "가사를 모르겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.14,
